{"tid":140911,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（認真）點樣有效解決便秘","createTime":"2017-03-02T13:53:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T13:12:58.000Z","uid":10081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d18ec78b5ef95cb70d229669e5a7a2ff747b4278","tid":140911,"uid":10081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:53:28.000Z","msg":"我不嬲都係一日最少屙一次屎，但係最近呢一個月突然有啲困難，每日都係得返平時份量嘅四份一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排狂食菜都無乜改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 買左啲便秘藥一食就有得屙，但係我只係幾日先食一次，唔想依賴左隻藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有同想經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099f2fbb4b8c7242f9b45c8ed4255cd3be85bbee","tid":140911,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"食次麻辣邊爐就搞掂啦"},{"pid":"2d2683b3f99975928a29ebca0debb9748eb9602f","tid":140911,"uid":86732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:00:04.000Z","msg":"一日一蘋果 / 做運動 等條腸郁下"},{"pid":"a9573ffcfb010de31f7304353e9bd29053b109ca","tid":140911,"uid":66926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"朝早飲凍奶茶"},{"pid":"7242c907d0b51a48fcbf94361d02f981e4922afb","tid":140911,"uid":10081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食次麻辣邊爐就搞掂啦</blockquote><br />\n少少辣都唔食得點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2fa69f15aa069a74ed060c2c17b9b89158b71d","tid":140911,"uid":10081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:25:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一