re":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"食菜之餘，食有油嘢食物都好緊要，唔好諗住係咁食菜就掂"},{"pid":"bf00c33c73f5735dc4807e0fddd198d6cff88783","tid":140911,"uid":65721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 飲杯凍奶茶 食串街邊小食乜撚都有得你柯啦係咪呀 啱唔啱呀"},{"pid":"2cd2d8b31f7ca74e42476c8d371d47e8200313f8","tid":140911,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:05:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d88d11fa6de1523137bda308e0eda2a39f4c7a6","tid":140911,"uid":10840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:07:04.000Z","msg":"最近娘親買左啲水果粉俾我沖，飲左幾日，日日都有屎屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0719bc52b3b800679e0d5fd86bb885447a40bb8d","tid":140911,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:10:27.000Z","msg":"我黎解答啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人類排便就好似擠牙膏 <br />\n<br />\n要擠出黎 要有力度，入面有足夠體積<br />\n<br />\n力度方面，補充蛋白質可以幫手<br />\n<br />\n但亦有人係大腸缺乏calcium/vitaminB complex 令<br />\n<br />\n到大腸抽蓄 控制唔到力度<br />\n<br />\n大便既體積就好睇Fibre量吸收啦，另外就係水份<br />\n<br />\n食多D易痴牙既菜，千奇唔好食生菜呢D呃自己既菜<br />\n<br />\n仲有一種較少見係缺鐵性既便秘 不過你做左上面講<br />\n<br />\n果D先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd90d3bc03baf5e42459050dc8da8f76f1c752c9","tid":140911,"uid":33040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:11:07.000Z","msg":"認真 一早餐飲奶茶包柯"},{"pid":"45567d9b7bb041ceb8e25412c07eecbf787325a8","tid":140911,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"順帶一提 世衛話一日最少屙兩次先係正常<br />\n屙得一次已經係輕微便秘"},{"pid":"24e67d7d3062671df38346e3eda7b435cdcd4360","tid":140911,"uid":58583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:12:35.000Z","msg":"肴望大家唔好用D咩偏方令自己肚瀉咁傻<br />\n<br />\n用番正常方法先係全面健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04410a1d851ca50d005e07dea5c793cf3b7e53eb","tid":140911,"uid":10081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>m記早餐+凍奶茶</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喺英國讀緊書，得勁淡嘅茶包加奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140c16313c5e29e01a099c6d7df564d71b7783e3","tid":140911,"uid":10081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:54:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食菜之餘，食有油嘢食物都好緊要，唔好諗住係咁食菜就掂</blockquote><br />\n有油唔係會難消化啲嘮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba96e8d661eba4c2829c24f1d6c85b681c0e2a58","tid":140911,"uid":10081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T16:57:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我黎解答啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人類排便就好似擠牙膏 <br />\n<br />\n要擠出黎 要有力度，入面有足夠體積<br />\n<br />\n力度方面，補充蛋白質可以幫手<br />\n<br />\n但亦有人係大腸缺乏calcium/vitaminB complex 令<br />\n<br />\n到大腸抽蓄 控制唔到力度<br />\n<br />\n大便既體積就好睇Fibre量吸收啦，另外就係水份<br />\n<br />\n食多D易痴牙既菜，千奇唔好食生菜呢D呃自己既菜<br />\n<br />\n仲有一種較少見係缺鐵性既便秘 不過你做左上面講<br />\n<br />\n果D先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我日日食西蘭花算唔算痴牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係summer 返intern 先做到朝早返工屙同放工食完飯屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d6b9ad90ac9ec43f80369c4b67c2de37edc0b5","tid":140911,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"信我，我由細到大都係7日先痾一次，睇過晒中西醫都無用，後來的發現左兩個方法好work。<br />\n<br />\n1) 自殺式飲可樂法，限定自己一分鐘內飲完330ml可樂，半個鐘內應該有得痾，不過未經訓練好可能會係口到爆返出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2) 每日一個橙，要新鮮好食嘅細橙，每日一個，對頭髮/便秘/皮膚都有極大改進。"},{"pid":"c9032bb7d8d5e0822578ab4c61a12a676dbccd14","tid":140911,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我黎解答啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人類排便就好似擠牙膏 <br />\n<br />\n要擠出黎 要有力度，入面有足夠體積<br />\n<br />\n力度方面，補充蛋白質可以幫手<br />\n<br />\n但亦有人係大腸缺乏calcium/vitaminB complex 令<br />\n<br />\n到大腸抽蓄 控制唔到力度<br />\n<br />\n大便既體積就好睇Fibre量吸收啦，另外就係水份<br />\n<br />\n食多D易痴牙既菜，千奇唔好食生菜呢D呃自己既菜<br />\n<br />\n仲有一種較少見係缺鐵性既便秘 不過你做左上面講<br />\n<br />\n果D先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我日日食西蘭花算唔算痴牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係summer 返intern 先做到朝早返工屙同放工食完飯屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩菜好介紹，我成日以為生菜有用添"}]}